    <title>Silicon Labs Series 2 Devicetree helpers</title>
    <innerfile refid="common-clock_8h">common-clock.h</innerfile>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Devicetree macros for clock enables and clock branches on Silicon Labs Series 2 devices, for use with the <computeroutput>silabs,series-clock</computeroutput> binding.</para>
<para><computeroutput>CLOCK_BRANCH_*</computeroutput> macros represent clock branches, while <computeroutput>CLOCK_*</computeroutput> macros represent clock enables. </para>
